uesday\">#GivingTuesday</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23EndViolenceAgainstWomen\"><br />\n</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>December</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>1: <a href=\"http://www.worldaidsday.org/\">World AIDS Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldAIDSDay&amp;src=typd\">#WorldAIDSDay</a></strong><a href=\"http://www.worldaidsday.org/\"><br />\n</a><strong>3: <a href=\"http://www.idpwd.com.au/\">International Day of People with Disabilities</a>\u00a0&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23IDPwD\">#IDPwD</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23IDPWD\"><br />\n</a><strong>5: <a href=\"http://www.volunteeractioncounts.org/en/\">International Volunteer Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23VolunteerDay\">#VolunteerDay<br />\n</a>5: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/soilday/\">World Soil Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldSoilDay\">#WorldSoilDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23IVD2014\"><br />\n</a><strong>9: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/anticorruptionday/\">International Anti-Corruption Day </a>&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23AntiCorruptionDay\">#AntiCorruptionDay</a></strong><a href=\"http://www.worldaidsday.org/\"><br />\n</a><strong>10: <a href=\"http://www.ohchr.org/EN/AboutUs/Pages/HumanRightsDay.aspx\">International Human Rights Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23HumanRightsDay\">#HumanRightsDay</a></strong><br />\n<strong>11: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/mountainday/\">International Mountain Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23mountainday\">#MountainDay<br />\n</a>18: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/migrantsday/\">International Migrants Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23MigrantsDay\">#MigrantsDay</a></strong></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><stron